comments: Es muy difcil pero un clase muy interesante.
I would tell everyone to take this course.

Professor Reymundi is extremely competent and understanding. She genuinely cares that you learn the material and will help you do well in the class, and the students can all feel that. The class follows the typical structure of language classes, but Professor Reymundi makes this one great
It's the next language class, so about what you'd expect. Very similar structurally to 120, with more focus on depth rather than breadth when discussing topics.
If you're interested in Spanish take it, great class.
